  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Accounts Executive",
  "description": "<p>Full set of accounts for month end &amp; year end closing (AP, AR, GL, CB)  </p>\n<p>Handle subcontractors' accounts and payment  </p>\n<p>In charge of project progress billing, receipts, project budget and profit recognition  </p>\n<p>Scrap sales, interco and ad hoc billing  </p>\n<p>Handle ATTC (Approved training &amp; testing center) transaction  </p>\n<p>Giro payment entries, perform bank reconciliation, manage bank balance  </p>\n<p>Prepare monthly accounts schedule  </p>\n<p>Responsible for monthly closing of accounts including preparing accounts schedules  &amp; journal entries  </p>\n<p>Prepare monthly financial reports and variance analysis  </p>\n<p>Analyse cost and the actual performance compared to budgets  </p>\n<p>Prepare management reports  </p>\n<p>Handle quarterly GST submission  </p>\n<p>Tax and statutory audit compliance  </p>\n<p>Assist in any adhoc reporting as and when required  </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Requirements : </p>\n<p>Diploma in Accounting  </p>\n<p>Minimum 3 years of relevant working experience and preferably with experience in  construction companies would be an added advantage  </p>\n<p>Strong commitment and dedication to strict adherence to reporting deadlines  </p>\n<p>Ability to work independently and meticulously with high level of motivation  </p>\n<p><br></p>",
